         <div type="translation" resp="#jmr" xml:lang="en">
            <p><note>i</note>: To our lord Flavius Claudius Constantine, most noble and excellent Caesar <note>all erased</note>.</p>
            <p><note>ii</note>: To our Lord Flavius Julius Constantius Pius, Felix, always Augustus. </p></div>
        
         <div type="translation" source="#tantillo2010" xml:lang="it">
            <p>Al nostro signore Flavio Claudio Costanzo (?) nobilissimo e fiorentissimo Cesare. Al nostro signore Flavio Giulio Costanzo,
               Pio Felice per sempre Augusto . . . ?</p></div>
         <div type="translation" source="#lsa" xml:lang="en"><p>To our lord Flavius Claudius Constantius, most noble and most prosperous Caesar.</p>
            <p>To our lord Flavius Iulius Constantius, pious, fortunate, eternal Augustus.</p></div>
         
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>A dedication to Constantius Gallus (later erased) and Constantius II.</p>
